item.title: We Play, You Play: Sonic Frontiers with Jordan Morris
item.description: Heather, Nick and Matt are joined by return guest Jordan Morris to discuss the latest 3D Sonic entry Sonic Frontiers! They talk about Sonic running up giant robots, the open world, the epic soundtrack, fishing with Big the Cat and more! Check out Jordan's comic in Chilling Adventures Presents... Pop’s Chock’lit Shoppe of Horrors coming March 22nd, 2023. Pre-order here: https://previewsworld.com/Catalog/JAN231229 Follow us on Twitter and Instagram @getplayedpod... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/afafh2s6
